high_descs: Turn right, move in between a sink and a diningtable, and face the diningtable.
Pick up a butterknife from the diningtable.
Take a tiny step to the right.
Cut the banana on the table with the butterknife.
Turn around and approach the sink.
Put the butterknife in the sink.
Go back to the diningtable.
Pick up a banana slice from the diningtable.
Step back to the sink.
Put the banana in the sink, rinse it out, and pick it up again.
Step to the right of the sink and look at the countertop.
Put the banana on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed-out banana on the countertop.

high_descs: walk over to the dining table.
pick up the butter knife from the table.
walk over to the other side of the table that the fruit is on.
use the knife to cut the banana.
walk over to the sink.
put the knife in the sink.
walk back over to the dining table.
pick up a slice of banana from the table.
take the banana and walk to the sink.
wash the banana and then remove it from the sink.
walk around to the other side of the sink on the countertop.
put the banana on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: get a knife and cut a banana and then bring to the countertop.

high_descs: Turn right towards the large white dining table.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Look at the banana near the center of the table.
Slice the banana up.
Turn to the sink opposite the long end of the table.
Put the butter knife inside the sink.
Turn back to the banana.
Pick up one slice of the banana.
Turn back to the sink.
Wash the banana slice in the sink and pick it back up.
Go towards the end of the counters to the left of the sink.
Put the banana down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed banana slice on a kitchen counter.
